## 12-INVARIANT CHECKLIST (MUST PASS ALL)

1. `FHE.allowThis(variableName)` after every write to an encrypted state variable?
2. Zero `if()`, `require()`, or `assert()` on FHE handles or comparison results?
3. Zero synchronous `FHE.decrypt()` in production contract code?
4. `FHE.fromExternal(input, proof)` called before EVERY use of an external input?
5. Async decryption uses `makePubliclyDecryptable` + `checkSignatures`?
6. ACL grants (`allow`, `allowThis`) match the Privacy Specification exactly?
7. Zero `externalEuintXX` (unvalidated handles) stored in state?
8. All `finalize*` functions guarded against replay (`require(!_finalized)`)?
9. View functions return encrypted handles, not decrypted values?
10. Token contracts MUST extend `ERC7984`?
11. Two-step SDK init used in frontend/backend (`initSDK` then `createInstance`)?
12. `userDecrypt` signature uses exactly 8 arguments as per `@zama-fhe/relayer-sdk`?

